# Generated outputs: keep the figures (PNG) and the small summary/parameter
# tables (CSV) in the repo as a record of the results, but exclude the large
# raw per-observation forecast dumps and the multi-hundred-MB stdout logs.
*.png
!exampleQRF.jpg
!exampleQGB.jpg
!exampleGAS.jpg
!exampleHYBRID.png
!output/*.png
output/*_forecasts.csv
output/*stdout*.txt

